[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1222","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Netbt.sys 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统的 Netbt.sys（NetBIOS over TCP/IP 驱动）存在拒绝服务漏洞。该组件在处理 DNS 主机名解析结果时未对返回数据进行充分校验，当远程恶意 DNS 服务器针对主机名查询返回 0.0.0.0 这一异常 IP 地址时，Netbt.sys 会因解析逻辑缺陷触发系统崩溃（蓝屏）。攻击者需能够控制或劫持目标系统所使用的 DNS 服务器，使其返回特制的 0.0.0.0 响应，即可在无需身份认证的情况下远程诱导 Windows NT 4.0 主机崩溃重启，造成服务不可用。该漏洞影响所有运行 Windows NT 4.0 且依赖 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 解析的网络主机，攻击前提为目标主机向受攻击者操控的恶意 DNS 服务器发起主机名查询。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1222"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.753","remediation":"建议立即为 Windows NT 4.0 安装微软官方安全补丁（升级至 Service Pack 4 及以上版本，该补丁已修复 Netbt.sys 解析 0.0.0.0 导致的崩溃问题）。若无法立即升级，应在网络边界防火墙限制仅允许使用受信任的内部 DNS 服务器，阻断来自不可信外部 DNS 服务器的响应，并禁用或限制 NetBIOS over TCP/IP 以临时缓解远程拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q188/5/71.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3893","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1222","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2d0833866f347223eab80ef68cc3e2461a4e724d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8/GHSA-2wcg-78mh-f9m8.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87559/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1222.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001008.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1010","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1206","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10819,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10841}}","description":"SystemSoft SystemWizard 软件包在 HP Pavilion（Windows 98）及其他可能存在的平台和操作系统中安装了两个被标记为\"对脚本安全\"（safe for scripting）的 ActiveX 控件。由于这两个控件（Launch 控件与 RegObj 控件）被浏览器信任可用于脚本操作，未经验证的远程攻击者只需构造一个恶意网页并引用上述控件，即可在访问该页面的用户上下文中执行任意系统命令。攻击条件为受害者使用易受影响的浏览器访问攻击者控制的网页，无需身份认证或本地权限。该漏洞影响装有 SystemWizard 的 HP Pavilion 等 Windows 98 设备，攻击者可借此实现远程代码执行与系统控制权夺取。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1206"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.753","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 HP Pavilion 随机附带的 SystemSoft SystemWizard 组件中标记为\"safe for scripting\"的 Launch 和 RegObj 两个 ActiveX 控件（在 IE 中通过\"管理加载项\"禁用或设置 kill bit 注册表项 {对应 CLSID} 为 0x00000400），并将 Windows 98 升级至厂商后续修复版本或弃用该预装软件；临时缓解可在 IE 安全设置中将\"对未标记为可安全脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化和脚本运行\"设为禁用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93336970231857&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/555","http://www.systemsoft.com/l-2/l-3/support-systemwizard.htm","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1206","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1206.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg/GHSA-gjmg-cjcp-mhwg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/555/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1206.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001007.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1010.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1177","title":"nph-publish 目录遍历任意文件写入漏洞","description":"nph-publish 1.2 之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可在上传操作的文件路径名中使用 ..（点点）序列实现目录跳转，从而覆盖服务器上任意文件。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需身份认证，攻击者仅需构造特制的上传请求即可触发，可能导致 Web 服务文件被篡改或恶意文件写入，影响系统完整性和可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1177"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.990","remediation":"立即将 nph-publish 升级到 1.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复路径遍历问题。如无法升级，应在服务器端对上传路径参数进行严格过滤，拒绝包含 `..` 的路径字符串，并将上传目录限制在非 Web 可访问的独立目录中。建议迁移至仍在维护的 Web 服务器软件作为最终解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-genome.wi.mit.edu/WWW/tools/CGI_scripts/server_publish/nph-publish","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2055","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1177","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/a2f3ff3fa5db5c7705ebd942909ec114df063700/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/nph-publish.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1175","title":"Cisco IOS Cache Engine WCCP 身份验证缺失漏洞","description":"Cisco Cache Engine（用于 Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本）中的 Web 缓存控制协议（WCCP）缺乏身份认证机制，远程攻击者无需任何鉴权即可向目标设备的 UDP 2048 端口发送特制 WCCP 数据包，从而将原本指向合法服务器的 HTTP 流量重定向至攻击者控制的任意主机，进而实现中间人攻击、流量劫持或敏感信息窃取。该漏洞影响大量早期 Cisco 网络设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1175"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.753","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 到 11.3 或更高版本（该版本起 WCCP 支持 MD5 认证），并在网络中配置 ACL 限制 UDP 2048 端口的来源 IP 仅为受信任的缓存引擎设备，拒绝来自外部的 WCCP 流量。如无法升级，可在边界防火墙上丢弃发往 UDP 2048 的非授权数据包作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-054.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/wccpauth-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1577","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1175","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cisco-sa-19980513-wccp-auth.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001005.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71565265-4d4c-43b5-9801-c1bbf5c6174a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0996","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1167","title":"Third Voice Web Annotation 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Third Voice Web Annotation 注释工具存在跨站脚本（XSS）安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在注释内容中注入恶意 JavaScript 脚本，当其他用户浏览包含恶意注释的页面时触发该漏洞，从而导致攻击者能够窃取用户的敏感会话数据、窃取身份认证凭据或生成伪造的网页内容实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响了 Third Voice Web Annotation 用户的数据机密性和完整性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1167"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.783","remediation":"立即卸载 Third Voice Web Annotation 浏览器插件，该软件已停止维护且无官方安全更新。作为通用缓解措施，在 Web 应用中启用 Content-Security-Policy HTTP 响应头（如 script-src 'self'），并对所有用户输入实施严格的输出编码（HTML实体编码），防止恶意脚本注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7252.php","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20636%2C00.html","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20677%2C00.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1167","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1167.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83040/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0988","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1157","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 TCP/IP ICMP Subnet Mask 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 TCP/IP 协议栈组件 tcpip.sys 在处理 ICMP 子网掩码地址请求（Subnet Mask Address Request）数据包时存在缺陷。当目标系统在同一网络接口上绑定了多个 IP 地址时，远程攻击者可向该主机发送特制的 ICMP 子网掩码请求报文，触发协议栈处理异常，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 之前版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，但需目标系统配置多 IP 地址作为前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1157"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.523","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 tcpip.sys 对异常 ICMP Subnet Mask Address Request 报文的处理逻辑。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙或路由器上过滤入站的 ICMP Subnet Mask 地址请求报文（类型 17、代码 0）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q192/7/74.ASP","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3894","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1157.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1157.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1157","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/115c94bd1da3cc18977d652d6e78c9f4a5dfc13b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1157.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1157.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2pvc-9pxf-rw8p/GHSA-2pvc-9pxf-rw8p.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86277/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1157.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0988.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0980","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1148","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及更早版本的 FTP 服务存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过与目标 FTP 服务器同时建立大量被动（PASV）连接，耗尽服务器连接资源，导致正常服务不可用。该漏洞利用复杂度低、无需特殊权限，影响安装了 IIS 4.0 FTP 服务的 Windows NT 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1148"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.420","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS98-006 (KB189262) 提供的更新补丁，该补丁限制了对 IIS 线程池的过度消耗。如无法安装补丁，建议将 FTP 服务与 WWW 服务分离到不同服务器，避免 FTP 连接耗尽导致 Web 服务中断；同时配置防火墙限制 FTP 端口的并发连接数，并监控系统事件日志中大量 \"Passive connect timed out\" 告警以识别攻击源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q189/2/62.ASP","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1215","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1148.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1148","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1148.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1148.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xr94-m5ww-76cc/GHSA-xr94-m5ww-76cc.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1148.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1148.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001002.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/839e2559933f5ff6cd50b4768fd382827d790668/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0978","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1132","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Routing Information Field 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 在处理 Token Ring 网络的源路由转发信息时存在缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统发送路由信息字段（RIF）中跳数超过 7 的特制数据包，或者包含重复 Token Ring ID 的列表，触发异常处理错误导致系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1132"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.313","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对此漏洞发布的安全更新（KB Q179157），该补丁限制了 Token Ring 源路由数据包中 RIF 跳数及重复 ID 的处理。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。临时缓解措施可在网络边界防火墙或路由器上丢弃源路由选项（Loose Source Routing 和 Strict Source Routing）的 IP 数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90763508011966&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90760603030452&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q179/1/57.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1399.php","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1132.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1132.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1132","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1132.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1132.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3cw4-pq4g-xq2f/GHSA-3cw4-pq4g-xq2f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1132.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--39d3e7ff-2b55-479e-90b9-e099e1c741c0.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0978.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0959","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1124","title":"Allaire ColdFusion HTTP Client 访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"ColdFusion 的 HTTP Client 应用存在安全绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 mainframeset.cfm 应用提交目标页面参数，利用服务器端请求转发机制访问受限制的 Web 页面。由于该请求从服务器本地发起，访问控制机制无法有效拦截，导致攻击者能够绕过端口级别的访问限制，获取本应受保护的非授权资源。该漏洞影响 Adobe ColdFusion 相关版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1124"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.283","remediation":"升级 ColdFusion Server 至官方修复版本（4.5.1 及以上），或移除/重命名 `mainframeset.cfm` 文件阻断代理请求路径。临时缓解措施为在 Web 服务器层（如 IIS）配置 URL 访问规则，禁止外部请求访问 `mainframeset.cfm`，并在防火墙规则中限制 ColdFusion 服务对外部内网端口的出站连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstorm.securify.com/mag/phrack/phrack54/P54-08","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1124","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/3508ccc52a2baed6a1946843005e8957c7067f39/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-11xx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/fc6f74915c306ca5f0e8feb3a1630bc318e69157/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/3254b0243059843609b70bbf6d468af5b834d86d/api/1999/CVE-1999-1124.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1124.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0959.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0957","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1117","title":"IBM AIX lquerypv 本地文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1 及 4.2 版本中 lquerypv 工具存在任意文件读取漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 -h 命令行参数指定任意文件路径，导致系统敏感信息泄露。该漏洞源于程序未对用户传入的文件路径参数进行充分过滤，攻击者拥有本地账号即可利用，影响范围有限但可读取 /etc/passwd 等敏感文件。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1117"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.383","remediation":"升级至 AIX 5.1 及以上版本以彻底修复该漏洞；若无法升级，安装 AIX 4.2.1 对应 APAR 补丁 (IX68465)。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod 750 /usr/sbin/lquerypv` 限制 lquerypv 仅 root 和 system 组可执行，或移除该文件的 setuid 权限 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lquerypv`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420195&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&w=2&r=1&s=lquerypv&q=b","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/455","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19345","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1117","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1117.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76/GHSA-g9xm-g3q5-pm76.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1117.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2965ee5f-33dd-4bc7-9bea-43e0e83e5800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/0b7b3d855cd8fca7b800fb29d6754e2da82897b6/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0957.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0947","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1105","title":"Microsoft Windows 95 Remote Administration 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Windows 95 在启用 NetWare 网络的远程管理和文件共享功能后，当管理员远程登录系统时会自动创建隐藏的 C$ 共享，远程攻击者可通过映射网络驱动器的方式访问该共享，从而读取目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，但需要管理员已远程登录过目标系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1105"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.947","remediation":"Windows 95 已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议立即升级至受支持版本的 Windows（如 Windows 10/11）。如无法升级，请禁用\"NetWare 网络远程管理与文件共享\"功能：控制面板 → 网络 → 服务中移除该组件；同时在防火墙中禁止 TCP 139/445 端口入站连接，并限制管理员远程登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7231.php","http://www.net-security.sk/bugs/NT/netware1.html","http://www.zdnet.com/eweek/reviews/1016/tr42bug.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/55853b6e755a0ecd08195e09435b787f0cba6bbe/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8/GHSA-rcfw-38c9-2wm8.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1105","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1105.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1105.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000996.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0947.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0942","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1102","title":"BSD lpr 符号链接攻击本地任意文件写入漏洞","description":"BSD 系列操作系统（包括 SunOS 4.1.1、BSD 4.3、A/UX 2.0.1 等）中的 lpr 行式打印服务存在任意文件写入漏洞。本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击，在反复调用 lpr 命令约 1000 次后，利用程序对临时文件处理不当的竞态条件，将任意内容写入或覆盖系统任意文件，从而可能导致权限提升或破坏系统完整性。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用需本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1102"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.580","remediation":"升级 lpr 到已修复符号链接竞争条件的版本，或替换为 LPRng/CUPS 打印系统。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户执行 lpr 的权限，将 lp 设备文件权限设为 0700，并监控 /tmp 目录的符号链接创建行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-25.shtml","http://www.aenigma.net/resources/maillist/bugtraq/1994/0091.htm","http://www.phreak.org/archives/security/8lgm/8lgm.lpr","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/94380d498cb52b65d051c9bd443b6f2aa85bf8ec/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1102","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1102.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx/GHSA-97ch-49wx-wfmx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88452/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1102.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--be2ec783-c4fb-40a3-9c11-0cb511dfa34f.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--be2ec783-c4fb-40a3-9c11-0cb511dfa34f.owl","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0942.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0940","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1100","title":"Cisco PIX Private Link 配置文件 DES 密钥强度漏洞","description":"Cisco PIX Private Link 4.1.6 及更早版本在处理配置文件中的特定命令时存在安全缺陷，导致 DES 加密密钥的有效长度从标准的 56 位被降低至 48 位。攻击者可通过暴力枚举攻击显著降低破解密钥所需的计算复杂度，进而解密受保护的通信链路。该漏洞影响使用 Cisco PIX Private Link 功能的所有早期版本设备，攻击者只需获取配置文件访问权限即可利用此弱点实施攻击，无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1100"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.327","remediation":"升级 Cisco PIX 防火墙软件至 4.1.7 或更高版本，该版本已修复 DES 密钥长度截断问题。如无法升级，应在配置中禁用 Private Link 的 DES 加密，改用 3DES 或 AES 等更强加密算法替代，并限制对配置文件的物理访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-056.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/pixkey-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1579"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0940.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0936","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0936.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1093","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JScript 脚本引擎缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 SP1 及更早版本中的 JScript 脚本引擎的 Window.External 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页触发该漏洞，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响早期 Windows 系统上的 IE 浏览器，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害较大。建议用户升级至更高版本的 IE 浏览器以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1093"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.420","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本即可消除此漏洞。如无法升级浏览器，可在 Internet 选项→安全→自定义级别中将「活动脚本」禁用作为临时缓解方案；建议停止使用 IE 内核浏览器，改用 Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器以避免遗留漏洞风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q191/2/00.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/1276.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-011","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1093","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1093.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2w6r-5vhj-25r3/GHSA-2w6r-5vhj-25r3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1093.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--01b36f88-506e-4fbb-9503-8cad88f7bb41.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88090/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0936.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0931","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0931.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1084","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 AEDebug 注册表项权限设置不当本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统中 AEDebug 注册表项权限设置不当，本地攻击者可修改该注册表项指向恶意调试器程序。当系统发生崩溃时，系统会自动执行该注册表项指定的调试器，从而以系统权限运行木马程序，导致机密性、完整性和可用性受损。攻击者需具备本地登录权限，无需额外认证即可利用此漏洞。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS00-008 中发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1084"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.253","remediation":"限制对注册表项 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\AEDebug 的写入权限，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的完全控制权，移除 Users 组的写入权限。建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），NT 4.0 已停止安全更新多年。可通过组策略或 regedit 的权限设置对该注册表项应用更严格的 ACL。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90222453431604&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q103/8/61.asp","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-029.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1044","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-008","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19798"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0931.toml"}]